.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

There are 5 different favourite colors: blue, green, red, white, yellow
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: folk, electronic, metal, soul, pop
5 different games are played: snooker, mah-jongg, domino, go, billiard
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: family, animation, sports, zombie, musical
The people use 5 different means of transport: bike, car, snowmobile, airplane, ship
1. the fan of folk is the person who likes red
2. the fan of swedish is the person driving the snowmobile
3. the fan of electronic is the person playing go
4. the person who likes green is on the left of the person who likes white
5. the person who likes green is the person playing mah-jongg
6. the person watching sports movies is the person driving the car
7. the person who likes yellow is the person watching animation movies
8. the person playing domino is in the middle
9. the fan of soul is on the far left
10. the person watching musical movies is on the left or right of the person driving the bike
11. the person driving the ships is on the left or right of the person watching animation movies
12. the person watching family movies is the person playing snooker
13. the fan of metal is the person watching zombie movies
14. the fan of soul is on the left or right of the person who likes blue
15. the person watching musical movies is on the left or right of the person playing billiard

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Color		|    yellow	|     blue	|      red	|     green	|     white	|
| Music-Genre	|   soul	|    electronic	|    folk	|    metal	|    swedish	|
| Transport		|     bike	|    ship	|     car	|     airplane	|      snowmobile	|
| Game	|    billiard	|     go	|     domino	|    mah-jongg	|      snooker	|
| Movie-Genre		|   animation	|    musical	|  sports	|    zombie	|   family	|
